# ImageSearchWebApplication

This project contains the code for a simple Image Search application that allows users to search for images using a keyword and view the results dynamically.

## Features
-- Search Functionality: Users can input a search term to find relevant images.
-- Dynamic Results: The application displays the search results with images and links to the original source.
-- Load More Results: Users can click on a "Show more" button to load additional search results.

## How It Works
-- Search Input: Users type a search term into the input field.
-- Search Button: Users click the "Search" button to initiate the search.
-- Displaying Results: The search results are displayed dynamically below the search form, including images and links to the original sources.
-- Show More Button: Clicking the "Show more" button loads additional images, enhancing the search experience.

## Files Included

index.html: The main HTML file containing the structure of the application.
style.css: The CSS file for styling the application.
index.js: The JavaScript file handling the search logic and dynamic content rendering.
Installation and Usage
